== Spanish ==

=== Etymology ===
Latin ''[[solere]]''

=== Verb ===
'''soler'''

# To be accustomed to doing something.  To do something on a regular basis.  Usually followed with an infinitive, e.g. ''suele llegar tarde'', "he usually arrives late".

